{"word":"προσλογίζομαι","slug":"προσλογίζομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προσλογίζομαι</b></el> <p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a>:<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to reckon</i> or <i>count in addition to</i>, <el>τί τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to impute</i>, <el>τί τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}